cmd comand to run it : 

1. Create a new folder for your project and navigate into it:

mkdir pdf_qa_app
cd pdf_qa_app


2. On Windows:

python -m venv venv
.\venv\Scripts\activate


3.Install the required libraries using the requirements.txt file:

pip install -r requirements.txt


4.Download the embedding model:

ollama pull nomic-embed-text


5.Download the LLM:

ollama pull gemma:2b

6.Run the Streamlit App
Now you're ready to launch the application. Run the following command in your terminal from the project directory (pdf_qa_app).

streamlit run app.py




direct run : 

python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\python.exe -m 
pip install -r ..\requirements.txt 
ollama pull nomic-embed-text 
ollama pull gemma:2b 
venv\Scripts\streamlit.exe
run ..\app.py
